							<div id="post-62945" class="post post-62945 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-economics category-inequality category-internet category-jobs category-workers tag-broadband tag-clark-merrefield tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-economy tag-merrefield tag-pandemic tag-research-roundup tag-rural-broadmand tag-telework tag-work-from-home">
