																								<li class="cat-post-item">
									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/internet/rural-broadband-coronavirus/" rel="bookmark" title="Rural broadband in the time of coronavirus">
										<span class="rthumb">
